plot: As Batwoman attempts to fight the proliferation of Snake Bite through Gotham, a random encounter forces Ryan to revisit her painful past; and she determines to ensure others like her don't go unnoticed.

Ryan goes on a personal mission, when a young boy asks Batwoman to find his missing brother. The mission brings back Ryan's memories of the past when she was all alone in the foster system except for her future lover, Angelique. Meanwhile, Sophie is forced to team up with Alice to try and find the mysterious Ocean - with some help from Luke.—Gislef
